---
title: Sweet Mustard Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Feta & Toasted Almonds
description: The secret's out - our sweet mustard spice blend takes chicken to next-level deliciousness! The oven does most of the work in this recipe, so it's ideal for busy weeknights - all you need to do is chop the veggies, flavour the chicken and toss the salad!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-pepper-chicken-feta-9ba26bee.jpg
